@startuml

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title SSH: conexiune unica, canale multiple (multiplexare)

actor Client
node "SSH Server" as S

Client -> S : TCP 22\nSSH transport (encrypted)

rectangle "In interiorul conexiunii SSH" {
  component "Channel: shell" as CH1
  component "Channel: exec" as CH2
  component "Channel: SFTP" as CH3
  component "Channel: port forward" as CH4
}

Client --> CH1
Client --> CH2
Client --> CH3
Client --> CH4
CH1 --> S
CH2 --> S
CH3 --> S
CH4 --> S

note right of S
Un singur TCP
canale logice multiple
fiecare cu flux separat
end note

@enduml
